data.title: Southeastern University
data.meta_description: Southeastern University offers more than 100 degree programs at the associate, bachelors, masters, and doctoral levels.
data.text:
SEU Worship — a collaboration between our faculty, staff, students, and alumni — is a reflection of the worship movement happening during our weekly campus chapel services and within our community.

Once you meet us, you’ll see right away why SEU is the perfect setting for this chapter of your story.

NOTICE OF NONDISCRIMINATORY POLICY AS TO STUDENTS

Southeastern University admits students of any race, color, national and ethnic origin to all the rights, privileges, programs, and activities generally accorded or made available to students at the school. It does not discriminate on the basis of race, color, national and ethnic origin in administration of its educational policies, admissions policies, scholarship and loan programs, and athletic and other school-administered programs.
